# Changelog

## [v0.0.3] - 2025-04-27

### Fixed

* Bug fix on logger

## [v0.0.2] - 2025-04-25

### Added

* APM package with tracing and metrics
* Errutil package with errors and error codes
* Method package with reflect methods

## [v0.0.1] - 2025-04-24

### Added

* Logger package with standard logger and custom logger
* Custom logger with file output
* Standard logger with json formatter
* Error, Info, Warn, Debug, Fatal, Panic log levels
* WithFields method for custom log fields
* SetLogLevel and SetLogFormatter methods
* processLog method for error handling

### Changed

* Updated logger package to use logrus
* Changed log levels to use logrus levels

### Removed

* Removed old logger package
